reviewText: I loved how I was able to experience Thousand Lakes and Elegy era songs live, with the band being as tight as it has ever been, and the singer's versatility switching from clean to gutural vocals with next to no effort blew my mind. Go buy it now. I got the 4 disc boxset, with 2 dvds and 2 live cds.

This is certainly one of the best live productions I have seen.
Well worth waiting for something of this standard.
